data.description:
move in ready!  Should be FHA & VA ready (ask your lender): new electrical panel box (no more fed pacific & roof less than 10 years old)--generator outlet installed in carport Spent fall of 2022 & 2023 doing improvements: used as a 4br...all have closets(tax card has as 3br) Improvements: new pump on water filtration system & new electrical panel box (both Sept 2023), new sliding doors, sentricon installed summer 2023, septic pumped & lines drained spring 2023. Major components have been replaced/updated. 
One level living brick charmer w/large detached garage (workshop, office, gym...endless options), spacious fenced back yard, inside washer & dryer hookup, open kitchen & dining area, covered back deck. Inside features den w/FP, dining area and open kitchen. Brick exterior w/metal roof (6yr old), hot water heater (4yr old), HVAC regularly serviced.  No flood insurance. Conv. located to major grocery, dining options, and quick trip to downtown Historic Bwk & FLETC. Shared water well is approx $150/per year.
